[
  {
    "text": "Oh, I am ready for a\ngood night's sleep.",
    "start": 0.0,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "What is going on?",
    "start": 4.46,
    "duration": 2.136
  },
  {
    "text": "[UPBEAT MUSIC]",
    "start": 6.596,
    "duration": 3.374
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on.",
    "start": 10.94,
    "duration": 0.69
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my spleen.",
    "start": 11.63,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "I think I got it.",
    "start": 12.77,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't got it.",
    "start": 13.61,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Crazy people!",
    "start": 14.27,
    "duration": 1.867
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, I feel like I'm\nin the womb again.",
    "start": 16.137,
    "duration": 1.583
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, I just had\nto wiggle a little bit.",
    "start": 17.72,
    "duration": 1.11
  },
  {
    "text": "That's great.",
    "start": 18.83,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "[KNOCKING ON DOOR]",
    "start": 23.67,
    "duration": 0.988
  },
  {
    "text": "Coming!",
    "start": 24.658,
    "duration": 2.472
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi sir, it's time to check out.",
    "start": 27.13,
    "duration": 1.55
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, OK.",
    "start": 28.68,
    "duration": 1.13
  },
  {
    "text": "[KNOCKING ON DOOR]",
    "start": 29.81,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "Dude!",
    "start": 31.82,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm working on it!",
    "start": 32.32,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Get out of your room!",
    "start": 34.52,
    "duration": 3.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Check out is at\n11:00, not 11:01.",
    "start": 38.42,
    "duration": 1.93
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no hey.",
    "start": 40.35,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "You guys think this is funny?",
    "start": 41.25,
    "duration": 1.37
  },
  {
    "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
    "start": 42.62,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Anything you leave will be sold.",
    "start": 43.78,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, that looks so good.",
    "start": 48.55,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "Too bad those Snickers\nare $18 apiece.",
    "start": 49.78,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no, no, no, did\nyou just open that?",
    "start": 52.6,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh yeah baby!",
    "start": 54.4,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Those are $7 apiece!",
    "start": 55.66,
    "duration": 3.657
  },
  {
    "text": "Lee, do you know anything?",
    "start": 59.317,
    "duration": 1.083
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 60.4,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "Why did you open that?",
    "start": 61.03,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "It's water!",
    "start": 62.33,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I can fix this.",
    "start": 62.83,
    "duration": 2.29
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, the seal is a dead giveaway.",
    "start": 65.12,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you have any gum?",
    "start": 66.83,
    "duration": 0.963
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I don't have gum,\nbut I have Swedish Fish.",
    "start": 67.793,
    "duration": 1.917
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no, no, stop!",
    "start": 69.71,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, let's look how\nmuch damage has been done.",
    "start": 72.65,
    "duration": 4.39
  },
  {
    "text": "It looks like three\nseals have been broken.",
    "start": 77.04,
    "duration": 3.05
  },
  {
    "text": "That's tap water.",
    "start": 80.09,
    "duration": 3.03
  },
  {
    "text": "Got them.",
    "start": 83.12,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "That's a Snickers.",
    "start": 86.53,
    "duration": 2.28
  },
  {
    "text": "$923.",
    "start": 88.81,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "What a night.",
    "start": 90.67,
    "duration": 0.81
  },
  {
    "text": "I wish I would have been\ninvited to the party.",
    "start": 91.48,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": "I can offer you guys,\nfor one night only,",
    "start": 95.56,
    "duration": 2.21
  },
  {
    "text": "our nonrefundable rooftop view.",
    "start": 97.77,
    "duration": 2.43
  },
  {
    "text": "Rooftop?",
    "start": 100.2,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "You guys are going to love it.",
    "start": 100.71,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "It has an insane\nview of the roof.",
    "start": 101.96,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "An insane rooftop view?",
    "start": 103.38,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "That's my guy.",
    "start": 104.46,
    "duration": 0.727
  },
  {
    "text": "Show me the rooftop!",
    "start": 105.187,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Show me the rooftop!",
    "start": 106.02,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, it is a rooftop view.",
    "start": 114.88,
    "duration": 2.07
  },
  {
    "text": "An insane view of the roof.",
    "start": 116.95,
    "duration": 1.33
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 118.28,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "From the roof?",
    "start": 118.78,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, pretty much.",
    "start": 119.29,
    "duration": 0.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 120.1,
    "duration": 0.24
  },
  {
    "text": "It's got a view of the rooftop.",
    "start": 120.34,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know what kind of\ntwisted wordplay business",
    "start": 121.42,
    "duration": 2.125
  },
  {
    "text": "you're running here,\nwhat I'm through with it!",
    "start": 123.545,
    "duration": 2.055
  },
  {
    "text": "We need another room!",
    "start": 125.6,
    "duration": 0.89
  },
  {
    "text": "36.",
    "start": 129.71,
    "duration": 0.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Should be right here.",
    "start": 130.52,
    "duration": 3.475
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 133.995,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I just came from 20.",
    "start": 140.03,
    "duration": 1.125
  },
  {
    "text": "[OMINOUS MUSIC]",
    "start": 141.155,
    "duration": 2.725
  },
  {
    "text": "There's no way this is right.",
    "start": 150.8,
    "duration": 2.91
  },
  {
    "text": "No way.",
    "start": 153.71,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "There she is, finally!",
    "start": 155.18,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "It's nice at least they give you\na few different pillow options.",
    "start": 159.92,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "[BALLOON POPPING]",
    "start": 162.86,
    "duration": 0.708
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 163.568,
    "duration": 1.764
  },
  {
    "text": "Know times are tough when\nthey're using cornhole bags",
    "start": 165.332,
    "duration": 2.208
  },
  {
    "text": "as decorative pillows.",
    "start": 167.54,
    "duration": 3.115
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 170.655,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 175.02,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Ow!",
    "start": 176.58,
    "duration": 2.51
  },
  {
    "text": "That's just weird.",
    "start": 179.09,
    "duration": 3.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa, whoa, whoa!",
    "start": 182.35,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no!",
    "start": 184.35,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "What is going on?",
    "start": 189.07,
    "duration": 1.41
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm taking the toiletries.",
    "start": 190.48,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "They're going to throw\nthem away anyways.",
    "start": 191.86,
    "duration": 1.708
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 193.568,
    "duration": 0.962
  },
  {
    "text": "Woo, q-tips!",
    "start": 194.53,
    "duration": 1.53
  },
  {
    "text": "We deserve these batteries.",
    "start": 196.06,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Triple A's.",
    "start": 197.26,
    "duration": 0.698
  },
  {
    "text": "Sending some stuff your way.",
    "start": 197.958,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "OK!",
    "start": 199.125,
    "duration": 0.535
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we go!",
    "start": 199.66,
    "duration": 1.425
  },
  {
    "text": "OK little of this,\nlittle of that.",
    "start": 201.085,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Little bit of that.",
    "start": 203.755,
    "duration": 1.215
  },
  {
    "text": "Last thing, I've always\nwanted a Sleep Number.",
    "start": 204.97,
    "duration": 2.092
  },
  {
    "text": "You think they'll\nnotice it's gone?",
    "start": 207.062,
    "duration": 1.458
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't think so.",
    "start": 208.52,
    "duration": 0.89
  },
  {
    "text": "OK.",
    "start": 209.41,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, place is great.",
    "start": 212.55,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah right, place is a cesspool.",
    "start": 214.29,
    "duration": 1.665
  },
  {
    "text": "Night, man.",
    "start": 220.05,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Ugh.",
    "start": 221.13,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "You're disgusting.",
    "start": 221.85,
    "duration": 1.11
  },
  {
    "text": "They should pay us\n$59.99 to stay here.",
    "start": 225.53,
    "duration": 4.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Hot tub, pool down there.",
    "start": 230.2,
    "duration": 1.393
  },
  {
    "text": "But what I'm most proud of is\nour state-of-the-art fitness",
    "start": 231.593,
    "duration": 2.417
  },
  {
    "text": "center.",
    "start": 234.01,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Pop those sleeves right up.",
    "start": 238.49,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Second thought, keep those down.",
    "start": 239.66,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Is it supposed to be doing this?",
    "start": 240.8,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "No, you're fine.",
    "start": 242.18,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "You're fine.",
    "start": 242.847,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "What's going on man?",
    "start": 245.667,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "I was just wondering if\nI can get an upgrade?",
    "start": 246.5,
    "duration": 1.875
  },
  {
    "text": "Doubt it.",
    "start": 248.375,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "But you can check though, right?",
    "start": 249.71,
    "duration": 2.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Nothing, dude.",
    "start": 252.29,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "Can I talk to the owner?",
    "start": 252.873,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm the owner's son.",
    "start": 253.873,
    "duration": 0.847
  },
  {
    "text": "That makes sense.",
    "start": 254.72,
    "duration": 1.11
  },
  {
    "text": "That makes the most sense.",
    "start": 255.83,
    "duration": 3.082
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, I'm not the guy who\ntypically calls in a noise",
    "start": 258.912,
    "duration": 2.167
  },
  {
    "text": "complaint, but it sounds\nlike a Civil War reenactment",
    "start": 261.079,
    "duration": 2.441
  },
  {
    "text": "next door.",
    "start": 263.52,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 264.74,
    "duration": 1.096
  },
  {
    "text": "[MARCHING BAND MUSIC]",
    "start": 265.836,
    "duration": 1.488
  },
  {
    "text": "[SHOUTING]",
    "start": 267.324,
    "duration": 2.976
  },
  {
    "text": "Hold the line!",
    "start": 272.284,
    "duration": 1.984
  },
  {
    "text": "For my family!",
    "start": 274.268,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "You got me [INAUDIBLE].",
    "start": 276.748,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "He's not going to make\nit, we got to leave him!",
    "start": 278.55,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Need a tourniquet!",
    "start": 280.91,
    "duration": 4.213
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm not going to make it!",
    "start": 285.123,
    "duration": 1.227
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey!",
    "start": 286.35,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, is this a Boy Scout hat?",
    "start": 286.85,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah it is.",
    "start": 288.09,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "OK.",
    "start": 288.59,
    "duration": 0.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Does it look OK?",
    "start": 288.96,
    "duration": 0.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Just flip it around, it looks\ntoo much like a Boy Scout.",
    "start": 289.2,
    "duration": 2.333
  },
  {
    "text": "There you go.",
    "start": 291.533,
    "duration": 1.677
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, good job everybody.",
    "start": 293.21,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's do it one more time.",
    "start": 294.21,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's switch sides.",
    "start": 295.33,
    "duration": 3.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Time for a shower.",
    "start": 298.63,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "Holy handles!",
    "start": 299.92,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Honey, have you seen the shower?",
    "start": 301.36,
    "duration": 1.89
  },
  {
    "text": "They got more nozzles\nin here than Home Depot!",
    "start": 303.25,
    "duration": 4.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Eeny, meeny, miny, moe.",
    "start": 307.45,
    "duration": 3.69
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa, it's so cold!",
    "start": 311.14,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Nope, that's not it.",
    "start": 314.08,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, wow.",
    "start": 315.28,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "The other one's kind of nice.",
    "start": 316.08,
    "duration": 1.208
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, God.",
    "start": 317.288,
    "duration": 1.577
  },
  {
    "text": "Medic!",
    "start": 318.865,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Honey, I need a lifeguard!",
    "start": 319.365,
    "duration": 1.155
  },
  {
    "text": "Turn it off!",
    "start": 320.52,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I want to go home!",
    "start": 321.02,
    "duration": 3.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi.",
    "start": 324.93,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "Checking in for two.",
    "start": 325.56,
    "duration": 0.93
  },
  {
    "text": "Just two?",
    "start": 326.49,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep, just the two of us.",
    "start": 327.24,
    "duration": 1.18
  },
  {
    "text": "He plays in the NBA.",
    "start": 328.42,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi.",
    "start": 329.41,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "We do have a two person\nmax capacity per room.",
    "start": 329.91,
    "duration": 2.105
  },
  {
    "text": "That's why it's\njust two, it felt",
    "start": 332.015,
    "duration": 1.375
  },
  {
    "text": "like an appropriate number.",
    "start": 333.39,
    "duration": 1.125
  },
  {
    "text": "Something just sneeze?",
    "start": 337.11,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "No, nothing sneezed.",
    "start": 338.55,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a tumor.",
    "start": 339.81,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't really like\nwhen people look at it.",
    "start": 340.68,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "So--",
    "start": 342.12,
    "duration": 0.42
  },
  {
    "text": "408.",
    "start": 342.54,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, thank you so much.",
    "start": 343.04,
    "duration": 1.07
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, boys, we're clear!",
    "start": 344.11,
    "duration": 2.29
  },
  {
    "text": "Ugh.",
    "start": 346.4,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Ow!",
    "start": 347.2,
    "duration": 1.31
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, man.",
    "start": 348.51,
    "duration": 2.632
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, those stairs were brutal.",
    "start": 351.142,
    "duration": 1.208
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, sorry about that.",
    "start": 352.35,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey man, you owe me 100.",
    "start": 353.55,
    "duration": 1.59
  },
  {
    "text": "You're over 50 pounds.",
    "start": 355.14,
    "duration": 1.02
  },
  {
    "text": "You were supposed\nto carry me on.",
    "start": 356.16,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "Housekeeping!",
    "start": 362.36,
    "duration": 0.852
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 363.212,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Clean towels!",
    "start": 363.712,
    "duration": 0.542
  },
  {
    "text": "No thank you.",
    "start": 364.254,
    "duration": 0.746
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's a pillow!",
    "start": 365.0,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Come back later\nwhen I'm not here!",
    "start": 365.667,
    "duration": 2.853
  },
  {
    "text": "What is happening?",
    "start": 368.52,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I said no!",
    "start": 369.87,
    "duration": 3.15
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on.",
    "start": 373.02,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "[KNOCKING ON DOOR]",
    "start": 373.74,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "Housekeeping!",
    "start": 374.49,
    "duration": 0.702
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 375.192,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I got an absolute smoking\ndeal on this room.",
    "start": 379.6,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Nice!",
    "start": 381.8,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "350 a night.",
    "start": 382.3,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Nice, 70 bucks a person?",
    "start": 383.68,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no, no, $3.50.",
    "start": 384.73,
    "duration": 2.31
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yeah.",
    "start": 387.04,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 388.16,
    "duration": 0.754
  },
  {
    "text": "OK.",
    "start": 388.914,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[OMINOUS MUSIC]",
    "start": 389.414,
    "duration": 3.346
  },
  {
    "text": "I hate to say it, dude,\nI feel like you overpaid.",
    "start": 392.76,
    "duration": 2.26
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, it is just\n70 cents a person.",
    "start": 395.02,
    "duration": 2.03
  },
  {
    "text": "Guys, it's for one night.",
    "start": 397.05,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "This'll be great.",
    "start": 398.37,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa!",
    "start": 399.72,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 400.28,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa.",
    "start": 400.78,
    "duration": 0.38
  },
  {
    "text": "That is way more comfortable\nthan I expected, huh?",
    "start": 401.16,
    "duration": 1.89
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll sleep right here.",
    "start": 403.05,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "T, what do you think\nthis pipe is, man?",
    "start": 404.01,
    "duration": 1.625
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know, AC overflow?",
    "start": 405.635,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "Something?",
    "start": 407.07,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "[CALMING MUSIC]",
    "start": 407.73,
    "duration": 2.958
  },
  {
    "text": "Dude, you stole\nall the tarp, man.",
    "start": 413.65,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "[TOILET FLUSHING]",
    "start": 419.508,
    "duration": 4.329
  },
  {
    "text": "Dude, what is that?",
    "start": 423.837,
    "duration": 1.183
  },
  {
    "text": "What is it?",
    "start": 425.02,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "Ty, what is that?",
    "start": 425.77,
    "duration": 1.155
  },
  {
    "text": "I had that all wrong, I'm\nreally sorry about that man.",
    "start": 426.925,
    "duration": 2.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Eggs, baby!",
    "start": 432.19,
    "duration": 1.137
  },
  {
    "text": "Woo-hoo!",
    "start": 433.327,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Get you some protein, Cory.",
    "start": 436.45,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "It's free.",
    "start": 437.77,
    "duration": 3.03
  },
  {
    "text": "OK.",
    "start": 440.8,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, sounds good man.",
    "start": 441.31,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "See you.",
    "start": 442.51,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, it's dark in here.",
    "start": 443.89,
    "duration": 1.345
  },
  {
    "text": "Where's the light\nswitch in this place?",
    "start": 445.235,
    "duration": 1.625
  },
  {
    "text": "That was a trash can.",
    "start": 449.74,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "It's got to be on\nthis wall, surely.",
    "start": 450.88,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Nope.",
    "start": 452.96,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 453.46,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, I really thought\nthat was going to be it.",
    "start": 456.63,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "No?",
    "start": 458.67,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 459.51,
    "duration": 0.54
  },
  {
    "text": "[CLAPPING]",
    "start": 460.05,
    "duration": 2.958
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes!",
    "start": 470.91,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 471.57,
    "duration": 1.303
  },
  {
    "text": "Ow!",
    "start": 472.873,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Just put it on the credit card.",
    "start": 476.918,
    "duration": 1.292
  },
  {
    "text": "Digits are 5189--",
    "start": 478.21,
    "duration": 1.45
  },
  {
    "text": "Shh!",
    "start": 479.66,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "60% of every hotel\nroom you stay in",
    "start": 480.91,
    "duration": 1.795
  },
  {
    "text": "has at least three hidden\ncameras or one audio monitoring",
    "start": 482.705,
    "duration": 2.375
  },
  {
    "text": "device.",
    "start": 485.08,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Honey, now's not a great time.",
    "start": 490.83,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Rage monster just\nchecked into our hotel.",
    "start": 492.08,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Got to keep tabs on him.",
    "start": 493.88,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Got way too much money\ntied up in this thing.",
    "start": 494.78,
    "duration": 1.875
  },
  {
    "text": "Over here, brother!",
    "start": 499.91,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!",
    "start": 500.87,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Audio tapping God's word?",
    "start": 502.91,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "You disgust me!",
    "start": 504.59,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't take these\nsafety precautions,",
    "start": 505.633,
    "duration": 1.667
  },
  {
    "text": "that's how you wake up\ntomorrow morning with eight",
    "start": 507.3,
    "duration": 1.31
  },
  {
    "text": "new images of you on\nGoogle walking around",
    "start": 508.61,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "in a pair of undies that\nyou're not proud of!",
    "start": 510.17,
    "duration": 1.875
  },
  {
    "text": "Think about this?",
    "start": 512.045,
    "duration": 2.315
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know.",
    "start": 514.36,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "What do you think?",
    "start": 515.4,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Just to be safe.",
    "start": 516.64,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 517.976,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Look behind you!",
    "start": 518.476,
    "duration": 0.966
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 519.442,
    "duration": 2.418
  },
  {
    "text": "We're onto you, you\ndirty rotten scumbags!",
    "start": 521.86,
    "duration": 1.89
  },
  {
    "text": "You didn't think we'd\nfind this one, did you?",
    "start": 523.75,
    "duration": 1.875
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 525.625,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, yeah, grab your\nstuff, grab your bags.",
    "start": 526.417,
    "duration": 1.833
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, let's just go.",
    "start": 528.25,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "We're coming for you!",
    "start": 529.292,
    "duration": 1.478
  },
  {
    "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
    "start": 530.77,
    "duration": 2.71
  },
  {
    "text": "How did we miss this?",
    "start": 533.48,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "We're going to find\nwhoever did this.",
    "start": 535.248,
    "duration": 1.542
  },
  {
    "text": "Time out.",
    "start": 539.466,
    "duration": 0.894
  },
  {
    "text": "Does it feel like you're running\nat an incredible rate of speed",
    "start": 540.36,
    "duration": 1.65
  },
  {
    "text": "down this hallway?",
    "start": 542.01,
    "duration": 0.44
  },
  {
    "text": "It really does, man.",
    "start": 542.45,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "We're stupid fast right now.",
    "start": 543.35,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's just go.",
    "start": 544.1,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Can't keep up.",
    "start": 544.94,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "We're getting close!",
    "start": 545.6,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "Where does that wire go?",
    "start": 546.59,
    "duration": 1.94
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 548.53,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Gar, get in here!",
    "start": 551.29,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "We found him!",
    "start": 552.25,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you doing spying on us?",
    "start": 555.52,
    "duration": 2.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Get out of here, get\nback to your room!",
    "start": 557.66,
    "duration": 1.85
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait a second.",
    "start": 559.51,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "Is that you Cody?",
    "start": 560.5,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 562.94,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "You sure?",
    "start": 564.38,
    "duration": 1.49
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes!",
    "start": 565.87,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "It's housekeeping!",
    "start": 566.37,
    "duration": 1.345
  },
  {
    "text": "He's gone.",
    "start": 575.91,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I think he went\nback to his room.",
    "start": 576.41,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "I think I did it!",
    "start": 579.35,
    "duration": 0.78
  },
  {
    "text": "You are so crazy!",
    "start": 588.545,
    "duration": 1.317
  },
  {
    "text": "You're going to pay for this!",
    "start": 589.862,
    "duration": 1.81
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 591.672,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Crazy!",
    "start": 592.172,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "How about a nice, cold drink?",
    "start": 592.672,
    "duration": 2.274
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 594.946,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "That's a fire sprinkler!",
    "start": 595.446,
    "duration": 1.434
  },
  {
    "text": "Make it rain!",
    "start": 596.88,
    "duration": 0.956
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you serious?",
    "start": 597.836,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "Stop!",
    "start": 598.77,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "All of our hotel rooms\nare getting flooded!",
    "start": 599.27,
    "duration": 3.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, the TVs.",
    "start": 603.07,
    "duration": 1.15
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on boys, you're\ncoming with me.",
    "start": 604.22,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "We're not done yet buddy!",
    "start": 606.02,
    "duration": 1.41
  },
  {
    "text": "That's my grandma's.",
    "start": 607.43,
    "duration": 2.39
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey!",
    "start": 609.82,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Is this a van Gogh?",
    "start": 610.32,
    "duration": 1.125
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!",
    "start": 611.445,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Then it's got to go!",
    "start": 611.945,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 612.778,
    "duration": 0.592
  },
  {
    "text": "That's--",
    "start": 613.37,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 613.87,
    "duration": 0.982
  },
  {
    "text": "Gaping hole in my van Gogh!",
    "start": 614.852,
    "duration": 2.948
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 617.8,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I've always wanted to do this.",
    "start": 618.76,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yeah!",
    "start": 621.08,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Full on rage!",
    "start": 623.48,
    "duration": 2.38
  },
  {
    "text": "This is unbelievable!",
    "start": 625.86,
    "duration": 1.69
  },
  {
    "text": "I love the Rage Monster.",
    "start": 627.55,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "I got to invest\nin something else.",
    "start": 628.89,
    "duration": 1.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Liked the meeting\nroom was better",
    "start": 639.755,
    "duration": 1.375
  },
  {
    "text": "than I thought I was going to.",
    "start": 641.13,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, y'all.",
    "start": 642.38,
    "duration": 0.52
  },
  {
    "text": "The doors, they\nlock on themselves.",
    "start": 642.9,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey could one of you help me--",
    "start": 644.7,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Super nice place.",
    "start": 649.915,
    "duration": 0.945
  },
  {
    "text": "I think they have room service.",
    "start": 650.86,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!",
    "start": 652.54,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa.",
    "start": 654.74,
    "duration": 1.41
  },
  {
    "text": "Locked out?",
    "start": 656.15,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 656.78,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "I've been there, brother.",
    "start": 657.53,
    "duration": 3.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Jean Carlos here to\ntake good care of you,",
    "start": 660.83,
    "duration": 2.255
  },
  {
    "text": "giving you a tip to all\nthe hottest places in town.",
    "start": 663.085,
    "duration": 2.125
  },
  {
    "text": "How about you give one back?",
    "start": 665.21,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Looking, looking, looking.",
    "start": 667.07,
    "duration": 2.1
  },
  {
    "text": "No seriously, I'm\nlooking for the tip.",
    "start": 669.17,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Ooh, a one.",
    "start": 671.84,
    "duration": 0.69
  },
  {
    "text": "I got one suggestion for you.",
    "start": 672.53,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "More!",
    "start": 673.74,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep on coming.",
    "start": 674.54,
    "duration": 0.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't be so mean to old Jean!",
    "start": 675.32,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "What rhymes with Jean?",
    "start": 677.12,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "How about a Benjamin.",
    "start": 678.5,
    "duration": 1.83
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes, one hundo!",
    "start": 680.33,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, enjoy your stay.",
    "start": 682.97,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "And if you need anything,\nfind somebody else.",
    "start": 684.18,
    "duration": 1.875
  },
  {
    "text": "Front desk.",
    "start": 690.03,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi, can I request a wake\nup call for 6:00 AM?",
    "start": 690.78,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah you sure may.",
    "start": 692.82,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "What level of intensity\nwould you like?",
    "start": 693.57,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "It's like a pad Thai\nrestaurant, 1 to 10 spice level.",
    "start": 694.8,
    "duration": 2.25
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't miss my flight,\nso level 10 I guess?",
    "start": 697.05,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Sanjur, we got a level 10-er!",
    "start": 700.89,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Please evacuate immediately.",
    "start": 707.42,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm up!",
    "start": 709.42,
    "duration": 3.5
  },
  {
    "text": "It's got an insane\nview of the roof.",
    "start": 712.92,
    "duration": 1.65
  },
  {
    "text": "From the roof?",
    "start": 714.57,
    "duration": 1.105
  },
  {
    "text": "Insane view of the roof, yeah.",
    "start": 715.675,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "From the roof?",
    "start": 716.925,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "From the roof?",
    "start": 717.508,
    "duration": 0.602
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, yeah, pretty much.",
    "start": 718.11,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "My guy.",
    "start": 719.31,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Unmatched view of the roof.",
    "start": 719.97,
    "duration": 1.232
  },
  {
    "text": "Can see the whole roof.",
    "start": 721.202,
    "duration": 0.958
  },
  {
    "text": "No way?",
    "start": 722.16,
    "duration": 0.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 722.7,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL RINGING]",
    "start": 723.9,
    "duration": 2.79
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi.",
    "start": 726.69,
    "duration": 1.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, it's what it looks like.",
    "start": 727.71,
    "duration": 2.27
  }
]